{"tid":192203,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友冇拉拉話冷靜下","createTime":"2017-04-08T11:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T16:11:15.000Z","uid":71964,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50790d1136a1252e59926aad63d442cbeddcb057","tid":192203,"uid":71964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:54:39.000Z","msg":"琴日係屋企Hea到夠鐘去睇戲既時候<br />\n女朋友話好攰 之後我見佢唔多開心<br />\n咪問下係咪唔舒服 結果佢喊起上黎<br />\n話唔睇戲啦 之後就番公司搵佢中學Fd傾下<br />\n仲Wts我比時間佢冷靜下 我Down左成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家都冇主動搵佢 應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢好好女仔黎 我地一見鐘情 <br />\n我呢排都冇做啲佢唔開心既事 好擔心佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該唔關其他男仔事 佢番學全女"},{"pid":"d2a0250dc2a93851441c953042b2d874631c594e","tid":192203,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:55:28.000Z","msg":"等分手"},{"pid":"2455fe33df963caff9466b0fd0b27d2ca47ec91d","tid":192203,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:56:14.000Z","msg":"關男仔事又好 唔關又好<br />\n記住莫強求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f80bf88a097cdf589bbab08aec86931fa9b990d","tid":192203,"uid":71964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關男仔事又好 唔關又好<br />\n記住莫強求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以咪唔想Chur佢 寧願忍住唔搵佢 都唔想好似比壓力佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313af8e86353442dfe5803b1c821d3f84ea540a1","tid":192203,"uid":5459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T12:01:54.000Z","msg":"佢係咪自己亂諗嘢諗埋一邊"},{"pid":"5135933b4dc3f2aa7a20cb2cdf5b81de1a4636ed","tid":192203,"uid":87404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T12:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161c85683bcc931f31052694df0ff6a221684153","tid":192203,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T12:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>關男仔事又好 唔關又好<br />\n記住莫強求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以咪唔想Chur佢 寧願忍住唔搵佢 都唔想好似比壓力佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />陣間佢話你唔搵佢即係唔關心佢唔掛住佢，直接分手<br />\n你而家唔挽留佢唔直接chur佢比個答案你，到最後所謂冷靜完咪又係分手，如果而家逼佢講清楚（即係你氹返佢），咪喺返埋咪好；如果而家搞到佢即分手，但佢分手後發現都係唔捨得你同返埋你一齊，咁都好；如果唔係，你比佢「冷靜」，咪又係等死..."},{"pid":"3d307363522f6153f95b1e3f860e2e378575143b","tid":192203,"uid":71964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T12:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係咪自己亂諗嘢諗埋一邊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知呀 但冇拉拉喊 應該發生啲嘢既"},{"pid":"4895b5524e8ab36e38dc8aa87daf18099fcea3b5","tid":192203,"uid":57617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T12:07:39.000Z","msg":"拉乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa04fa6e6c4df50e593610fe0f28df5db6f4946e","tid":192203,"uid":71964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T12:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>關男仔事又好 唔關又好<br />\n記住莫強求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以咪唔想Chur佢 寧願忍住唔搵佢 都唔想好似比壓力佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />陣間佢話你唔搵佢即係唔關心佢唔掛住佢，直接分手<br />\n你而家唔挽留佢唔直接chur佢比個答案你，到最後所謂冷靜完咪又係分手，如果而家逼佢講清楚（即係你氹返佢），咪喺返埋咪好；如果而家搞到佢即分手，但佢分手後發現都係唔捨得你同返埋你一齊，咁都好；如果唔係，你比佢「冷靜」，咪又係等死...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我形住 Wts佢=煩佢 所以有反效果<br />\n第二日啦 番工都番得好冇mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid