frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />陣間佢話你唔搵佢即係唔關心佢唔掛住佢，直接分手<br />\n你而家唔挽留佢唔直接chur佢比個答案你，到最後所謂冷靜完咪又係分手，如果而家逼佢講清楚（即係你氹返佢），咪喺返埋咪好；如果而家搞到佢即分手，但佢分手後發現都係唔捨得你同返埋你一齊，咁都好；如果唔係，你比佢「冷靜」，咪又係等死...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我形住 Wts佢=煩佢 所以有反效果<br />\n第二日啦 番工都番得好冇mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同我一樣<br />\n男朋友講冷靜<br />\n已經第五日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係我地冇嗌過交 冇嘈 希望佢處理完啲問題搵番我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04fee4fd605fcad28a2502d2837fb1103743cec","tid":192203,"uid":104265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"冇嘈交&ne;冇問題<br />\n可能你地之間有好多問題，但係佢一直都冇講<br />\n所以你應該係搵出問題嘅根源<br />\n而唔係齋等<br />\n就算你哋之後喺返埋一齊<br />\n啲問題依然存在<br />\n利申：親身經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e97fda59075151baea30626723aba7c39f2d635","tid":192203,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T12:37:13.000Z","msg":"我有朋友都係咁<br />\n突然間覺醒咁樣 話唔想同呢個人就咁過一世<br />\n<br />\n多口問句<br />\n係咪佢覺得你悶 唔識溝通?"},{"pid":"fac30753914e5395096e736134a4b0381c13b59c","tid":192203,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T12:39:19.000Z","msg":"坦白講 呢啲衰過有第三者<br />\n夠勇氣講出黎都預左無彎轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aaf714c58ffd5289683296e587b781392764fce","tid":192203,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T12:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94447ff5f4d93a1d6be2d46230d75d4ed05b9dde","tid":192203,"uid":99024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T12:41:28.000Z",